      "comment": "HURRICANE (2) steps out a further 85m to an untried trip. Strong winner last time by 8 lengths at Sandown in Grade 5 in the quickest time on the program (29.29). Looks the one to beat with even luck. VALENZUELA (6) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at 24 of 54 starts including 12 wins but missed the frame latest when fifth (30.01) over 520m at Cannington. Has a good record at this journey. Looks suited and expected to run well. OUTSIDES (8) had the drop on the lead from the inside before drawing clear to score (34.47) at Sandown in a Restricted WIN H over 595m. Will go close again if runs up to latest. ETHANOL SECRET (3) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
